p: LF carried out the cell culture, image analysis, and protein identification studies and drafted the manuscript. XY carried out the preparation of nano-Se and the study of two-dimensional electrophoresis and participated in the manuscript preparation. XR carried out the Se exposure and protein extraction study and performed the statistical analysis. YW conceived the study and participated in the design of the study. JL coordinated and helped to draft the manuscript. All authors read and approved the final manuscript.
